Frequently Asked Questions

Is MindWell a substitute for professional help?

No, MindWell is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult with a qualified healthcare provider.

How secure is my data?

We take data security seriously. All your information is encrypted and stored securely according to industry standards.

Can I delete my account?

Yes, you can delete your account and all associated data at any time through the settings page.
